snippet.title: Red Faction 2 GC trailer
snippet.description: Thats a trailer of the game Red Faction 2 for Gamecube. I don´t know how it feels on Gamecube because I only have it for computer. But on computer it is very good. It is better than the first Red Faction I think (I know the most find the first Red Faction better than the second but I´m not). You must know this is a beta version of the game this video shows so the graphics don´t look final and the weapons aren´t not finished and so on.
